# MINDFOLD LANDING PAGE — COMPLETE UI REPLICATION PROMPT

> Paste this entire prompt to any AI assistant (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, etc.) and it will recreate the exact same landing page UI for your product. Replace **[BRAND NAME]**, **[TAGLINE]**, **[DESCRIPTION]** and other bracketed placeholders with your own content.

---

## DESIGN SYSTEM & TOKENS

**Color Palette:**
- Background (all sections): `#f7f6f4` (warm off-white / light cream)
- Hero Scroll Section bg: `#ffffff` (pure white)
- Primary Dark (headings, buttons, icons): `#0a1128` (very deep navy/almost black)
- Body muted text / subtitles: `#5b637a` (slate grey-blue)
- White cards: `#ffffff`
- Card border: `rgba(0,0,0,0.05)` (very subtle)
- Section border: `rgba(0,0,0,0.05)`
- CTA primary button: `#0a1128` text `#ffffff`
- CTA secondary button: `#ffffff` bg, `#0a1128` text, `rgba(0,0,0,0.1)` border
- Popular badge: `#0a1128` bg, white text
- Feature icon colors (pastel):
  - Blue: bg `bg-blue-100`, icon `text-blue-600`
  - Purple: bg `bg-purple-100`, icon `text-purple-600`
  - Emerald: bg `bg-emerald-100`, icon `text-emerald-600`
  - Yellow: bg `bg-yellow-100`, icon `text-yellow-600`
  - Pink: bg `bg-pink-100`, icon `text-pink-600`
  - Indigo: bg `bg-indigo-100`, icon `text-indigo-600`
- Star ratings: `#facc15` (yellow-400), filled
- Avatar bg: `#0a1128`

**Typography:**
- Font family: **Geist Sans** (Google font: `Geist`) — clean, modern, geometric sans-serif
- Fallback: `system-ui, sans-serif`
- Heading style: `font-black` (900 weight), `tracking-tight`, `UPPERCASE`
- Hero H1: `text-7xl sm:text-8xl md:text-[8rem]` (massive display type)
- Section H2: `text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl`
- Section heading highlight (second word/phrase): same color but at 40% opacity (`text-[#0a1128]/40`)
- Card H3: `text-xl font-bold`
- Body/subtitles: `text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-[#5b637a]`
- Nav links: `text-sm font-medium`
- Buttons: `text-sm font-semibold`
- Custom scrollbar: 6px width, muted track, muted thumb with 3px radius

**Border Radius:**
- Cards: `rounded-[2rem]` (32px, very round pill-like corners)
- Buttons/pills: `rounded-full`
- Icon containers: `rounded-2xl` (16px)
- How-it-works icons: `rounded-[2rem]` (32px)
- Avatar circles: `rounded-full`
- Nav bar: `rounded-full`
- Pricing popular badge: `rounded-full`

**Shadows:**
- Cards: `shadow-sm`, upgrades to `shadow-md` on hover
- Highlighted pricing card: `shadow-2xl shadow-black/10`
- Navbar: `shadow-sm`
- How-it-works step icons: `shadow-sm`

**Global CSS Animations:**
```css
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes slideInLeft {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-20px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
}
/* Hover underline animation utility */
.hover-underline::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -4px; left: 0;
  width: 0; height: 2px;
  background-color: currentColor;
  transition: width 0.3s ease-in-out;
}
.hover-underline:hover::after { width: 100%; }
```

