## SECTION 1: NAVBAR

**Layout:** Fixed to the top of the viewport, centered horizontally, full-width container with `padding-top: 1rem`, acts as a floating pill nav bar.

**Container:** `fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50`, inner `max-w-5xl` centered nav pill.

**Nav pill styles:** `bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-lg border border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] shadow-sm rounded-full px-6 py-3 flex items-center justify-between`

**Left - Logo:**
- Dark square box `bg-[#0a1128] text-white p-2 rounded-xl` containing a Brain icon (Lucide `Brain`, 20x20)
- Next to it: brand name in `text-base font-bold text-[#0a1128]` + a tiny tagline below in `text-[10px] text-muted font-medium` ("By FRIEREN" or your sub-brand name) — stacked in a column

**Center - Navigation Links (hidden on mobile):**
- `hidden md:flex items-center gap-8`
- Links: Features, How It Works, Reviews, Pricing
- Style: `text-sm font-medium text-muted hover:text-foreground transition-colors`
- These are anchor links (`#features`, `#how-it-works`, `#reviews`, `#pricing`)

**Right - Auth Buttons:**
- "Log In" link: `text-sm font-medium text-muted hover:text-foreground transition-colors hidden sm:block`
- "Get Started" button: `text-sm font-semibold bg-black/5 text-[#0a1128] border border-black/10 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#0a1128] hover:text-white transition-colors` — pill shaped, goes from light grey to full dark on hover

