## SECTION 2: HERO SECTION

**Background:** `bg-[#f7f6f4]` (warm cream)
**Padding:** `pt-40 pb-32` (top padding accounts for fixed navbar)
**Layout:** Centered, flex column, `text-center`
**Max width:** `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`

**Badge (top pill label):**
- `inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-transparent border border-black/80 text-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[10px] tracking-widest font-semibold uppercase mb-10`
- Contains a small filled circle `w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-black rounded-full` as a dot indicator
- Example text: "AI-POWERED SELF REFLECTION" (replace with your badge text)

**Main Heading (H1):**
- `text-7xl sm:text-8xl md:text-[8rem] font-black tracking-tight text-[#0a1128] max-w-6xl mx-auto leading-none uppercase`
- Example: "LIFE IMITATES LIFE" — massive, bold, all-caps display heading

**Subtitle paragraph:**
- `mt-8 text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#5b637a] font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed`
- 1-2 lines describing the product

**CTA Buttons (mt-12, flex row, gap-4, centered):**

*Primary CTA:*
- `inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0a1128] text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-black transition-colors`
- Contains a right arrow icon (Lucide `ArrowRight`, 16x16) at the end
- Example: "Get Started Free →"
- Has a decorative **handdrawn arrow + "Click here" annotation** floating to the upper-left of the button (only visible on desktop/md+):
  - Positioned `absolute -left-[140px] -top-12`
  - SVG dashed curved arrow drawn in `#0a1128` stroke (strokeWidth 3.5, strokeDasharray "8 8")  
  - Arrow path: `M30,150 C40,110 80,90 90,120 C100,160 30,160 50,90 C60,55 90,40 140,50`
  - Arrowhead as filled triangle at the endpoint
  - Text "Click here" in `text-[28px] font-medium text-[#0a1128]` at `-rotate-[14deg]`, positioned below arrow
  - The whole element is `pointer-events-none opacity-90`

*Secondary CTA:*
- `inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-[#0a1128] border border-black/10 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 hover:border-black/20 transition-all shadow-sm`
- Contains a play icon (circle with play triangle inside, SVG drawn inline)
- Example: "Watch Demo"

