## SECTION 3: HERO SCROLL ANIMATION SECTION

**Background:** `bg-white`
**Effect:** A scroll-driven 3D tilt/parallax animation container (similar to Aceternity UI's `ContainerScroll` component).

**Title component (shown above the scrolling container):**
- Two-line heading:
  - Line 1: `text-4xl font-semibold text-[#0a1128]` — "Experience the future of"
  - Line 2 (large): `text-4xl md:text-[6rem] font-bold mt-1 leading-none` — "Mental Wellness"

**Content inside scroll container:**
- A **video player** (`<video>` tag) with `autoplay loop muted playsinline`
- `className="w-full h-full rounded-2xl object-cover object-left-top"`
- Video source: your product demo video file (e.g., `/dashboard-demo.mp4`)
- This video is displayed inside a tablet/screen mockup that tilts as the user scrolls

**Animation behavior:** As the user scrolls down, the view transitions from a tilted 3D perspective view to a flat, straight-on view of the screen content. This is a parallax-style ScrollContainer animation.

