## SECTION 4: FEATURES SECTION

**id:** `#features`  
**Background:** `bg-[#f7f6f4]`  
**Padding:** `py-24`  
**Max width:** `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`

**Section Header (centered, mb-20):**
- H2: `text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-[#0a1128] tracking-tight uppercase`
- Pattern: "[Normal text] [FADED text at 40% opacity]"
- Example: "Everything You Need for **MENTAL WELLNESS**" (where "MENTAL WELLNESS" is `text-[#0a1128]/40`)
- Subtitle: `mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#5b637a] font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed`
- Example: "Powerful tools designed to help you understand yourself better and take control of your mental health journey."

**Feature Cards Grid:**
- `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8`
- Each card: `bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-black/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300`

**Each card contains:**
1. **Icon box**: `w-14 h-14 [pastel-bg] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6`
   - Icon inside: Lucide icon `h-7 w-7 [pastel-text-color] strokeWidth={2.5}`
2. **Title**: `text-xl font-bold text-[#0a1128] mb-3`
3. **Description**: `text-[#5b637a] font-medium leading-relaxed`

**6 Features (adapt for your product):**
| # | Icon | Icon Color | Title | Description |
|---|------|-----------|-------|-------------|
| 1 | BookOpen | blue-100/blue-600 | Smart Journaling | Write daily entries and receive instant AI-generated reflections that help you understand your emotional patterns. |
| 2 | Brain | purple-100/purple-600 | Mental Health Metrics | Track 5 key metrics — mental health, happiness, accountability, stress, and burnout risk — scored from every entry. |
| 3 | BarChart3 | emerald-100/emerald-600 | Visual Analytics | Beautiful graphs and charts that show your wellness trends over time, helping you spot patterns and celebrate progress. |
| 4 | MessageCircle | yellow-100/yellow-600 | Ask Your Journal | Chat with an AI that has read your journal. Ask questions like 'Why do I feel stressed on Mondays?' and get real answers. |
| 5 | Users | pink-100/pink-600 | Therapist Connect | Browse verified therapists, book sessions, and share selected journal entries for more personalized professional support. |
| 6 | Shield | indigo-100/indigo-600 | Privacy First | Full control over what your therapist can see. Toggle visibility per entry, or disable sharing entirely. |

