## SECTION 5: HOW IT WORKS SECTION

**id:** `#how-it-works`  
**Background:** `bg-[#f7f6f4]`  
**Padding:** `py-24`

**Section Header (centered, mb-20):**
- H2: same style as Features section `font-black uppercase text-[#0a1128]`
- Pattern: "[Word] [FADED word] Works" — e.g., "How **MINDFOLD** Works"
- Subtitle: same style as Features

**Steps Grid:**
- `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8`
- Each step: `text-center group`

**Each step contains:**
1. **Step icon box**: `relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-white shadow-sm border border-black/5 text-[#0a1128] rounded-[2rem] mb-6`
   - Hover effect: `group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300` (lifts up on hover)
   - Lucide icon inside: `h-8 w-8 strokeWidth={2.5}`
   - **Step number badge**: `absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-[#0a1128] text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm`
2. **Title**: `text-xl font-bold text-[#0a1128] mb-3`
3. **Description**: `text-[#5b637a] font-medium leading-relaxed`

**4 Steps (adapt for your product):**
| Step | Icon | Title | Description |
|------|------|-------|-------------|
| 1 | UserPlus | Create Your Account | Sign up in seconds with just your name, email, and password. No credit card required to get started. |
| 2 | PenLine | Write Daily Entries | Journal about your day in up to 2000 characters. Our clean editor makes it easy to express your thoughts. |
| 3 | Sparkles | Get AI Insights | Our AI instantly analyzes your entry, generates a reflection, and scores 5 mental health metrics. |
| 4 | TrendingUp | Track Your Progress | Watch your metrics improve over time. Ask your journal questions and connect with therapists for deeper support. |

