## SECTION 7: PRICING SECTION

**id:** `#pricing`  
**Background:** `bg-[#f7f6f4] relative`  
**Padding:** `py-24`

**Section Header (centered, mb-20):**  
- Example: "Simple, Transparent **PRICING**"

**Pricing Cards Grid:**
- `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto items-end`

**Regular card:** `p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-black/5 bg-white hover:border-black/20 hover:shadow-lg shadow-sm transition-all duration-300`

**Highlighted/Popular card:** `border-2 border-[#0a1128] bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-black/10 z-10 md:scale-105` (slightly scaled up)
- Has a **"Most Popular" badge**: `absolute -top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-[#0a1128] text-white text-xs font-bold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm`

**Each pricing card contains:**
1. Plan name: `text-xl font-bold text-[#0a1128] mb-4`
2. Price: Large `text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#0a1128]` + `/mo` in `text-[#5b637a] font-medium`
3. Features list: `mb-8 space-y-4`
   - Each item: `flex items-start gap-3`
   - Checkmark: `w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#0a1128]/10 flex items-center justify-center` + Lucide `Check` icon `h-3 w-3 text-[#0a1128] stroke-[3]`
   - Feature text: `text-sm font-medium text-[#0a1128]`
4. CTA button: Full width, `py-3.5 rounded-full font-semibold`
   - Popular: `bg-[#0a1128] text-white hover:bg-black`
   - Regular: `bg-gray-100 text-[#0a1128] hover:bg-gray-200`
   - Text: "Get Started"

**3 Pricing Plans:**
| Plan | Price | Highlighted | Features |
|------|-------|-------------|----------|
| Basic | $9.99/mo | No | Daily journal entries, AI reflections, Mental health metrics, Ask Journal (Quick Reflect), Basic analytics |
| Intermediate | $14.99/mo | **Yes (Popular)** | Everything in Basic, Ask Journal (Deep Reflect), Advanced analytics & graphs, Therapist access, Session scheduling, Priority AI responses |
| Advanced | $24.99/mo | No | Everything in Intermediate, Unlimited AI conversations, Detailed mental health reports, Priority therapist matching, Session recordings & notes, Family wellness sharing |

