## FULL IMPLEMENTATION NOTES

### Framework & Stack
- **React/Next.js** is assumed; adapt accordingly for Vue, plain HTML, etc.
- Uses **Tailwind CSS v4** for styling (all classes shown are Tailwind utilities)
- Icons from **Lucide React** (`lucide-react` package)
- Font: **Geist Sans** via `next/font/google` (or load via Google Fonts CDN: `https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;900&display=swap`)

### Key Behaviors & Interactions
1. **Navbar is fixed**: appears over content, always visible on scroll
2. **Hover on feature cards**: `shadow-md` (subtle lift)
3. **Hover on step icons**: `-translate-y-2` (lifts up card image)
4. **Hover on pricing cards**: border darkens + shadow grows
5. **Primary nav button**: transitions from light `bg-black/5` to full `bg-[#0a1128]` on hover
6. **Scroll animation section**: 3D tilt parallax — content starts tilted (perspective transform) and straightens as user scrolls
7. **All section headings** follow the same two-part pattern: [Bold part] [Faded/dim part at 40% opacity] in UPPERCASE
8. **Consistent section spacing**: all content sections use `py-24` (6rem top+bottom)

### Content Customization
Replace these with your own content:
- `[BRAND NAME]` → your product name
- `[BADGE TEXT]` → short all-caps badge e.g. "AI-POWERED DOCUMENT PRINTING"
- `[HERO HEADLINE]` → massive display heading, uppercase, max 4-5 words
- `[HERO SUBTITLE]` → 1-2 sentence product description
- `[FEATURES]` → your 6 key features
- `[HOW IT WORKS STEPS]` → your 4 onboarding steps
- `[REVIEWS]` → your 6 testimonials
- `[PRICING PLANS]` → your 3 tiers

