## QUICK REFERENCE: Color Cheat Sheet

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--background` | `#f7f6f4` | All section backgrounds |
| `--foreground` | `#0a1128` | Headings, icons, dark elements |
| `--muted-text` | `#5b637a` | Subtitles, body text, footer text |
| `--card-bg` | `#ffffff` | All cards |
| `--card-border` | `rgba(0,0,0,0.05)` | Card borders |
| `--hero-scroll-bg` | `#ffffff` | Scroll animation section only |
| `--btn-primary` | `#0a1128` | Primary CTA buttons |
| `--btn-primary-text` | `#ffffff` | Primary CTA text |
| `--btn-secondary` | `#ffffff` | Secondary CTA background |
| `--btn-secondary-border` | `rgba(0,0,0,0.1)` | Secondary CTA border |
| `--star-color` | `#facc15` | Review star ratings |
